Source: masterkey-localindices
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Index Data <info@indexdata.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), maven2, default-jdk
Standards-Version: 3.8.0
Homepage: http://www.indexdata.dk/masterkey/

Package: masterkey-harvester
Architecture: all
Description: The LUI Harvester is a harvesting platform. It can harvest OAI-PMH, XML bulk and web crawl into a local unified index. It support splitting and XSL transformations. It supports Solr and Zebra as storages. The configuration is keept in a MySQL database. 

Package: masterkey-harvester-tomcat6
Architecture: all
Depends: tomcat6, masterkey-harvester
Description: Configuration of the LUI Harvester under Tomcat 6

